name: Component
notes: Software library or plugin, a comonent to be used in another tool or system

name: Project
description: Project without a significant software or service output

name: Script
notes: e.g. "glue code" integrating two or more functions from one or more tools or services

name: Software Package
description: Packaged software (typically for the desktop or mobile)

name: Standard
notes: Formally recognised information standard, or profile of a technology - e.g. a profile of a standard or protocol to constrain it to a particular use case or domain

name: System
notes: System providing a platform or environment with broad range of complementary functions. Note this is the system in the abstract sense - for actual running instances see 'services'.

name: Tool
notes: Piece of software providing single function, or narrow and highly integrated set of functions
